snippet.title: VA-11 HALL-A ● NA Release Trailer ● November 14th ● PS Vita
snippet.description:
The critically acclaimed cyberpunk bartending game makes its way onto PlayStation®Vita®! Releasing in North America on November 14th at $14.99. Also compatible with PS TV. Physical release printed and distributed by Limited Run Games! 

[PlayStation]
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0994-PCSE00756_00-VALHALLAPSVITA01

[Discord]
https://discord.gg/pXR8ND9

[Twitter]
https://twitter.com/wolfgameNA
https://twitter.com/SukebanGames
https://twitter.com/garoadmusic

[Web]
http://wolfgame.com/
http://sukeban.moe/

[Official VA-11 HALL-A Merch]
http://wolfgame.com/store.html

[More Games]
https://poppyworks.itch.io/

Recorded in Nashville, TN
Shot by Steven C. Knapp & Wolfgang Wozniak
Edited by Jaron Daughtry & Wolfgang Wozniak (https://twitter.com/ouren)
Composed by Michael Kelly
Arranged by Uriel Sage
Drums; Russ Glass
Bass; Michael Tebrinke
Piano; Kaitlyn Connor 
Guitar; Brandon salaway 
Sax; David Williford 
Engineered by Max Rupel 
Mixed by Michael Kelly
NA Boxart by koyoriin
